|======

| Name
| Type
| Mandatory
| Description


| etag
| boolean
| false
| Parameter which can be used to disable the etag parameter generation and thus increase performance when etags are not needed. Default: true. 

| fields
| string
| false
| Limit the output to certain fields. This is useful in order to reduce the response JSON overhead.

